  <description><![CDATA[<p>Peschiera's one of the most relaxed towns on Lake Garda and fantastic for family holidays. Despite being quite large, it has a very laid back feel and it isn't packed with tourists, unlike some of the more well-known resorts. The town has a real charm to it. There are some great walks along the River Mincio – the footpaths follow the old medieval walls. The centre's completely pedestrianised with lots of shops to browse and riverside cafés to stop off for a drink. </p>
<p style="color: #00533a;"><strong>What to see on a Peschiera holiday</strong></p>
<p>Peschiera's a great base – it’s one of the only two towns in Lake Garda with a train station so you can easily get to <a data-udi="umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b}" title="Verona">Verona</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice</a>. There are regular ferries to all resorts in the south of the lake and you can use the bus to get to the north. There are also two beaches that are around a ten-minute walk from the centre so you can have family day by the lake. Alternatively, fuel your family's adrenaline with a trip to Gardaland or Caneva World, both are a short bus ride away- the children will love it!</p>
<p>Discover more things to see and do in <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a>.</p>
<p style="color: #00533a;"><strong>Why book a holiday to Peschiera with Inghams?</strong></p>
<p>We've got some good quality hotels that offer great value for money. Your holiday is <a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">in safe hands</a> with Inghams.</p>]]></description>
